com.facebook.buck.event.external.elements

Interface TestResultsExternalInterface<T>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    TestResults

    public interface TestResultsExternalInterface<T>
    Describes the results of a set of tests from a specific target. This type is intended to be used by external applications (like the Intellij Buck plugin) to deserialize events coming from the webserver.
